lead_paragraph: The Toronto Blue Jays have acquired right-hander Mike Bolsinger from the Los Angeles Dodgers for right-hander Jesse Chavez and $1.15 million.

headline.print_headline: Blue Jays Acquire Bolsinger From Dodgers for Chavez, $1.15M
